    "Do not commit API keys or secrets. Always read them from environment variables (e.g., OPENAI_API_KEY) and never hard-code them.",
    "For styling, follow the existing approach in the project (Tailwind CSS or CSS-in-JS or plain CSS). If the project uses Tailwind utility classes, continue that pattern.",
